<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=4302&amp;p=36102#p36102"><![CDATA[
The very little I know - while the ppu is fetching tiles from 1000h, the A12 is up (bg or sprites). When the loopy_v has A12 toggled through 2006/7, yes, A12 is up.<br /><br /><span style="font-size: 75%; line-height: normal">...and I dislike getting "ignored". <img src="http://forums.nesdev.com/images/smilies/icon_sad.gif" alt=":(" title="Sad" /></span><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=39">Zepper</a> — Tue Aug 19, 2008 3:23 pm</p><hr />
